1. *Ubiće* ga ako ne poštuje pravila. (They will kill him if he doesn't follow the rules.) 
2. Oni će se boriti do ubića. (They will fight till death.) 
3. On će na kraju ubiću. (He will eventually kill her.) 
4. Njegov otac ga je ubiće. (His father killed him.) 
5. *Ubili* su mnogo ljudi. (They killed many people.) 
6. *Ubijali* su ih svakog dana. (They killed them every day.)